{"type":"finding","iteration":2,"id":"S1-02-abortable-sleep-helper","dimension":"D1","focus":"S1-02","summary":"loop-cli-main's shared sleep helper clears its timeout on abort, removes its abort listener on normal completion, rejects with signal.reason, and pairs with a named 200ms chunk constant.","sourceRefs":[".opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/external/loop-cli-main/src/shared/sleep.ts:1",".opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/external/loop-cli-main/src/shared/sleep.ts:7",".opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/external/loop-cli-main/src/shared/sleep.ts:11",".opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/external/loop-cli-main/src/config/constants.ts:13"],"targetFile":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/sleep.ts","supportFiles":[".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/README.md"],"portDifficulty":"easy","tag":"quick-win","whyItHelps":"Gives deep-loop-runtime one cancellation-safe sleep primitive instead of repeated raw timer cleanup across process runners and pool logic."}
